title: Nikita Zhustyev
text:
Nikita Sergeyevich Zhustyev (; born 23 November 2002) is a Russian <a href="association%20football">football</a> player who plays for <a href="FC%20Irtysh%20Omsk">FC Irtysh Omsk</a>.
Club career.
He made his debut in the <a href="Russian%20Football%20National%20League">Russian Football National League</a> for <a href="FC%20Irtysh%20Omsk">FC Irtysh Omsk</a> on 5 September 2020 in a game against <a href="FC%20Neftekhimik%20Nizhnekamsk">FC Neftekhimik Nizhnekamsk</a>.
